org.anchoranalysis.plugin.io.bean.task

Class CombineCSV

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<Task<T,S>>
      • Task<FileInput,CSVWriter>
        • CombineCSV

  • public class CombineCSV
extends Task<FileInput,CSVWriter>
    Combines multiple CSV files into a single CSV file.

    No check occurs that the same number of rows/columns exist in the files being combined.

    The following outputs are produced:

    Output NameDefault?Description
    combinedyesA CSV combining the input CSV files.
    inherited from Task
    Author:
    Owen Feehan
